title: Alexander's of Winchester
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A modern specialty tea shop close to the center of Winchester. In addition to a wide range of teas, sells coffee and other drinks as well as a variety of sandwiches and cakes. The shop also sells loose leaf teas and a small range of gifts. The cafe usually has vegan cake on offer (try the carrot cake) and plant milks. Please inquire about other possible vegan items or ones that can be made vegan.
